  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      More and more parents decide to maintain pregnancy which could have been interrupted because
      of serious fetal pathologies.

      In this observational study, we examine obstetrical and pediatric evolution of these
      pregnancies, from 2006 to 2016 in Montpellier University Hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
